{"tid":878891,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔仔開心到極!!【身體語言】+室內養會長壽!","createTime":"2018-10-27T13:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T05:20:40.000Z","uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4bee5074a429937977a18409b35e3f4704ae18","tid":878891,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"兔子跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。當牠們binky 時，這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。兔子也會舒適地躺在地上，伸展手腳，還會打翻騰。兔子在室內飼養會比室外養長命，因為沒有任何天氣和敵人威脅，感到安全、平靜和舒適。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會嚇驚兔子。以下2個videos 可以看到兔子最開心的時候：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=BBMsXovDUggW2io7Z2ScBYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6912d205\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE90ikFGQTqs&d=BBMsXovDUggW2io7Z2ScBYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=949cfc85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>資訊來源: <a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/did-you-say-binky/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Fdid-you-say-binky%2F&d=BBMsXovDUggW2io7Z2ScBYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=0a824b40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/did-you-say-binky/</a></strong>"},{"pid":"28b9c1aa870ca596c75f98fcf8683d70295df936","tid":878891,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}